{
 "name": "RPlog_Shenner_Comes_to_Palanhi",
 "title": "Shenner Comes to Palanhi",
 "summary": "Amid a blinding sandstorm at the Palanhi City starport, the Jedi Luke Skywalker and the conflicted Jessalyn Valios are loading the freighter Black Dragon when Luke's young protege Shenner -- disguised as a boy and searching ship to ship -- stumbles out of the wind looking for him. Reunited inside the Dragon, the sand-blinded Jessalyn is tended to by Luke while Shenner reports that her enigmatic employer Grathix wants to speak with Luke about Han Solo. As Shenner heads off to fetch Grathix and Luke steps out to check on Artoo, Princess Leia and Jessalyn are left alone, and a raw, embarrassed Jessalyn finally blurts out her confusion and anger over Luke having kissed her. Leia, startled but composed, gently navigates the confession just as an oblivious Luke returns, leaving the matter unresolved before she departs to check on Winter.",
